{"tid":2194143,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯今次拒簽夏域斯！一心一意簽另1人","createTime":"2020-09-08T10:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T15:39:37.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c91bb95ac11beb12ce55afa671679f8af377a468","tid":2194143,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"　　車路士花費8900萬英鎊的超高價格，簽下了利華古遜紅星夏域斯（Kai Havertz），這引起了不小的轟動。就這個價格，還是在曼聯拒絕抬價的前提下創造的。<br />\n<br />\n　　《曼徹斯特晚報》披露，曼聯今夏有機會簽下夏域斯，但紅魔拒絕加入這名球員的爭奪戰，他們當時一心一意的在爭奪辛祖（Jadon Sancho）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　利華古遜對夏域斯的標價達到8900萬英鎊，多蒙特對辛祖的標價是1.08億英鎊，不過曼聯覺得價格都不划算，沒有採取進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n　　上個賽季，夏域斯為利華古遜出場45次，攻入18球，貢獻9個助攻。最終，他選擇了誠意最足的車路士。"},{"pid":"0d9b339b2d1ea6eeb45dd72e5b300bd05fad3420","tid":2194143,"uid":119729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"夏域斯是誰？<br />\n辛祖才是真命天子"},{"pid":"fafd5da8c78baab1d719416414c153d491cb5ad5","tid":2194143,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"非英人對我曼可有可無"},{"pid":"aa8b8a82527eb201e6d94dc899350e9a0a016740","tid":2194143,"uid":63913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"車狗又買水貨，成億買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要上年數據一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7103bd7317edf6e7f7a017dd95771b1920fde559","tid":2194143,"uid":43827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"我曼要既你地一個都攞唔到 <br />\n唔要既你地可以攞去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81728080ca88b6a00c82d301c93dce964e2481b","tid":2194143,"uid":373119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8b8a82527eb201e6d94dc899350e9a0a016740","tid":2194143,"uid":63913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score